{
  "stem": "1581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But my friends dragged me back into the barracks, and somehow I-- I survived, and I came to, and I was in the labor-- in the work detail the next morning because you couldn't stay home.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "If you would stay home, you was shipped out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was impossible to survive on the rations that you get-- you got, and that was the purpose of it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This whole system was designed that you should work as much as you had in you, but the end result was death.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was slave labor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We were slaves.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That means we had absolutely no law or recall of any kind in our favor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were stripped of any human dignity you can imagine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We were exposed to the most sadistic, incredible indignities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were beaten.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We were pushed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We were tortured.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And of course enemy number one was this incredible hunger, which was with us 24 hours a day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And with it came the depression and the despondency, and a lot of people just couldn't take it, and they gave up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And you could see if one became marked that he's not going to be around any longer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "He became very pale, and he was swelling up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He had a swollen face, he had swollen legs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He became unbelievably fatigued, and we had trouble keeping him up at the appel and on the march to the place.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And whenever a man became what was-- what we called a muselman, a muselman was the one marked for death to come soon.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Invariably, it was only a few days, and they were dead.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And not only we knew it, but they knew it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Whoever was a muselman knew this is his end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they took their arrangements for their death.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
